Summary: Solid black disc. A light in the center, sourrounded by darkness, then, an outer ring of lights.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting on the front porch. I'm a sky watcher. I noticed a bright light moving south. I had no idea what it was, there weren't any navigation lights, and it was going pretty fast on a straight course. it was a round, black abject with a light in the center, and a ring of lights surounding the disc. It moved from north to south, and then it disappeared. It didn't shock me, I've seen things before.
